{
  "title": "linux网络",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">ifconfig eth0 显示一个以太网卡的配置&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">ifup eth0 启用一个 'eth0' 网络设备&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">ifdown eth0 禁用一个 'eth0' 网络设备&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">ifconfig eth0 192.168.1.1 netmask 255.255.255.0 控制IP地址&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">ifconfig eth0 promisc 设置 'eth0' 成混杂模式以嗅探数据包 (sniffing)&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">dhclient eth0 以dhcp模式启用 'eth0'&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">route -n 显示路右边</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">route add -net 0/0 gw IP_Gateway 配置默认网关</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">route add -net 192.168.0.0 netmask 255.255.0.0 gw 192.168.1.1 配置静态路由表 '192.168.0.0/16'&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">route del 0/0 gw IP_gateway 移除静态路由&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">echo \"1\" &gt; /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward 激活IP路由</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">hostname 显示系统的hostname</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">host www.example.com 解析域名的地址</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">nslookup www.example.com 解析域名地址</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">ip link show 显示所有网络接口的链接</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">mii-tool eth0 显示</span><font face=\"宋体, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">eth0的网络链接状态</span></font></font><div><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">ethtool eth0 显示eth0的网络统计数据</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">netstat -tup 显示所有活动连接和它的PID&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">netstat -tupl 显示所有监听服务和它的PID&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">tcpdump tcp port 80 监视所有HTTP的流量</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">iwlist scan 显示无线网络链接</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">iwconfig eth1 显示一块无线网卡的配置</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">whois www.example.com 在Whois中搜索域名信息&nbsp;</span></font></div>"
    }
